          <td height="45" VALIGN="TOP" bgcolor="#333333"><div class="topictitle"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width=100%>
      <tr>
       <td>
	   <div align="left" class="storytitle">Vanguard March Beta Newsletter Leaked</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storyauth">By Fricka</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storydetail">Tue, 14 Mar 2006, 18:55:00</div>
    
       </td>
       <td align=right valign=top>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="mailto:?subject=Vanguard%20March%20Beta%20Newsletter%20Leaked&body=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesafehouse.org%2Fnews%2FVanguard%2Fnews_255.php">Email&nbsp;this&nbsp;article</a></div>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="http://www.thesafehouse.org/news/Vanguard/printer_255.php">Printer&nbsp;friendly&nbsp;page</a></div>
	   <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="/cgi-bin/news/exec/goforum.cgi?id=255&cat=23">Discuss this story</a></div>
	  </td>
